      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=TASK:\nYou are the Orchestrator Agent (Manager). Build an enterprise-ready SEO content plan for the topic.\n\nINPUT:\nTopic: {{ $json.topic }}\nLanguage: {{ $json.language }}\nCountry: {{ $json.country }}\n\nREQUIREMENTS:\n- Expand the topic into a semantic keyword cluster: primary keyword, search intent, long-tail keywords, LSI terms.\n- Generate ONE best SERP query for competitor research.\n- Output must be valid JSON matching the output schema.\n\nReturn ONLY JSON.",
