      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=TASK:\nYou are the Researcher Agent (Worker).\n\nINPUT:\nTopic: {{ $json.topic }}\nPrimary keyword: {{ $json.output.primaryKeyword }}\nSERP results (JSON):\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.serpResults) }}\n\nGOAL:\n- Select the BEST {{ $json.maxSources }} sources for factual grounding and competitor analysis.\n- Prefer authoritative sources and high relevance.\n- Output JSON with selectedSources (url, title, reason).\n\nReturn ONLY JSON.",
